{"segment":5,"line_start":400,"line_end":499,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"追问","listener":null,"text":"黄蓉见他神色犹疑，追问道：","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":400,"line_end":400},{"speaker":"char_huang_yao_shi","speaker_name":"黄药师","listener":null,"text":"黄药师道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":408,"line_end":408},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"中虽如此","listener":null,"text":"他口中虽如此说，对欧阳克的狂妄已颇感不满，不愿多提此事，转头向洪七公道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":410,"line_end":410},{"speaker":"char_hong_qi_gong","speaker_name":"洪七公","listener":null,"text":"我来向你求一件事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":414,"line_end":414},{"speaker":"char_hong_qi_gong","speaker_name":"洪七公","listener":null,"text":"你别答允得太快，只怕这件事不易办。\"黄药师笑道：","tone":"微笑","chapter":18,"line_start":420,"line_end":420},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"七公拍手","listener":null,"text":"洪七公拍手笑道：","tone":"微笑","chapter":18,"line_start":422,"line_end":422},{"speaker":"char_huang_yao_shi","speaker_name":"黄药师","listener":null,"text":"黄药师道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":424,"line_end":424},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"洪七公笑","listener":null,"text":"洪七公笑道：","tone":"微笑","chapter":18,"line_start":430,"line_end":430},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"欧阳锋奇","listener":null,"text":"欧阳锋奇道：\"喝喜酒？\"洪七公道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":432,"line_end":432},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"靖与黄蓉","listener":null,"text":"指着郭靖与黄蓉道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":434,"line_end":434},{"speaker":"char_hong_qi_gong","speaker_name":"洪七公","listener":null,"text":"洪七公道：\"药兄，有这等事么？\"黄药师道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":442,"line_end":442},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"七公沉脸","listener":null,"text":"洪七公沉脸道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":444,"line_end":444},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"向欧阳锋","listener":null,"text":"转头向欧阳锋道：","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":446,"line_end":446},{"speaker":"char_hong_qi_gong","speaker_name":"洪七公","listener":null,"text":"洪七公道：\"你可知道还有一人不答允？\"欧阳锋道：","tone":"陈